Even the older &#39;470 I have uses digital pulses on the VT pin, so I 
wasn&#39;t able to sweep it it like 469. I haven&#39;t checked the other 
hack models yet. If anyone has these, and has a socpe, just look at 
the VT pin, if the radio has one, and see what it does when the 
radio is tuned.

 Frank-S



